definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in West Berkshire district, Berkshire , England ( OS grid ref SU4073 ) .
A village and civil parish in West Northamptonshire council area, Northamptonshire , England , previously in Daventry district ( OS grid ref SP6480 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
